📦 Core Dependencies (Maven pom.xml)
Add these blocks to your service-level pom.xml files to enable the microservices features:

1. Spring Cloud (Service Discovery & Gateway)
XML
<dependency>
    <groupId>org.springframework.cloud</groupId>
    <artifactId>spring-cloud-starter-netflix-eureka-client</artifactId>
</dependency>
<dependency>
    <groupId>org.springframework.cloud</groupId>
    <artifactId>spring-cloud-starter-gateway</artifactId>
</dependency>
2. Database & Persistence (PostgreSQL & Redis)
XML
<dependency>
    <groupId>org.springframework.boot</groupId>
    <artifactId>spring-boot-starter-data-jpa</artifactId>
</dependency>
<dependency>
    <groupId>org.postgresql</groupId>
    <artifactId>postgresql</artifactId>
    <scope>runtime</scope>
</dependency>
<dependency>
    <groupId>org.springframework.boot</groupId>
    <artifactId>spring-boot-starter-data-redis</artifactId>
</dependency>
3. Reporting & Security (RBAC & PDF/Excel)
XML
<dependency>
    <groupId>org.springframework.boot</groupId>
    <artifactId>spring-boot-starter-security</artifactId>
</dependency>
<dependency>
    <groupId>org.apache.poi</groupId>
    <artifactId>poi-ooxml</artifactId>
    <version>5.2.3</version>
</dependency>
<dependency>
    <groupId>com.itextpdf</groupId>
    <artifactId>itextpdf</artifactId>
    <version>5.5.13.3</version>
</dependency>
🐳 System Requirements (Environment)
Include this section in your README to tell users what they need installed on their machine to run the portal:

Java Development Kit (JDK): 17 or 21

Build Tool: Maven 3.8+

Database: PostgreSQL 14+ and Redis 7.0+

Containerization: Docker & Docker Compose (Recommended for running all services)

IDE: IntelliJ IDEA or VS Code with Spring Boot Extension Pack
